sc_cat_item.description:
The Dell XPS 13 Laptop is a compact yet powerful system offering high performance, durability and battery life in a small 13 inch package.

The machine comes pre-configured with access to all company IT ressources and includes the standard software package:

  • Microsoft Office with Outlook
  • ACME Sales Toolbox App
  • ACME Time Tracking App
  • Global VPN client

This item is offered with full support, warranty and service for 36 months.
